               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gәṣṣәw, Lectionary for the entire year (fols. 3ra-91vb)&#xD;
I-1) Scriptural readings with Psalms for liturgical periods, fasts and feasts (for the entire year) (fols. 3ra-40rb; 59ra-91vb)&#xD;
- Liturgical period called Yoḥannәs: fols. 3ra-6ra&#xD;
- Feasts of the Minor Prophets (Näbiyat Ṣadәqan): fols. 6ra-8rb&#xD;
- Liturgical period Masqal: fols. 8rb-11ra&#xD;
- Liturgical period Ṣәge: fols. 11ra-12va, 14ra-16vb&#xD;
- Liturgical period Sәbkät: fols. 12va-14ra&#xD;
- Liturgical period Lәdät: fols. 16vb-19rb&#xD;
- Feast of the Epiphany (Ṭәmqät): fols. 19rb-21ra&#xD;
- Feast of the Wedding of Cana (Qana za-Gälila): fols. 21ra-22vb&#xD;
- Feasts of Mary (za-ʾәgziʾtәnä): fols. 22vb-26rb&#xD;
- Feasts of the Martyrs (Sämaʿtat): fols. 26rb-28va&#xD;
- Feasts of the Righteous Ones (Ṣadәqan): fols. 28va-31vb&#xD;
- Fast of the Apostles (Ḥawaryat): fols. 31vb-36ra&#xD;
- Feats of Angels (Mälaʾәkt): fols. 36ra-40rb&#xD;
- Incarnation (Mäggäbit 29): fols. 59ra-60ra&#xD;
- Transfiguration (Däbrä Tabor): fols. 60ra-62va&#xD;
- 8th Sunday before Easter, Sunday of “He who descended…” (za-wärädä…) or “of the Encounter with the Fast” (Qäbbäla ṣom): fols. 62va-65va&#xD;
- 7th Sunday before Easter, Sunday “of the Holy” (Qәddәst): fols. 65va-67vb&#xD;
- 4th Sunday before Easter, Sunday “of the Mount of Olives” (Däbrä Zäyt): fols. 67vb-70va&#xD;
- 3rd Sunday before Easter, Sunday “of the Good Servant” (Gәbәr ḫer): fols. 70va-72vb&#xD;
- Palm Sunday (Hosaʿәna): fols. 72vb-76ra&#xD;
- Maundy Thursday (Ṣalota Ḫamus): fols. 76ra-77vb&#xD;
- Resurrection (Tәnśaʾe): fols. 77vb-80va&#xD;
- Sunday after Easter (Fäṣṣämnä…): fols. 80va-82vb &#xD;
- Ascension (ʿƎrgät): fols. 82vb-86rb&#xD;
- Pentecost (Ṗaraqliṭos): fols. 86rb-88va&#xD;
- Liturgical period Kәrämt (“Rainy season”): fols. 88va-90ra&#xD;
- Blessing prayer (Bakәkännä ʾƎgziʾo… “Bless us, Lord…): fols. 90vb-91vb&#xD;
I-2) Scriptural readings for the days of the week (fols. 40rb-59ra)&#xD;
- Monday (sänuy): fols. 40rb-43vb&#xD;
- Tuesday (śälus): fols. 43vb-46ra&#xD;
- Wednesday (räbuʿ): fols. 46ra-48va&#xD;
- Thursday (ḥamus): fols. 48va-50rb&#xD;
- Friday (ʾarb): fols. 50rb-52ra&#xD;
- Saturday (qädamit sanbat): fols. 52ra-54vb&#xD;
- Sunday (ʾǝḥud): fols. 54vb-59ra&#xD;
&#xD;
Additiones 1-2; colophon.</summary>
